    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（これはだいぶ落ち込んでるな……）\n（でも、慰めるよりmihoさんには……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（ She's taking this pretty hard… ）\n（ But rather than comfortin'‚ for miho-san… ）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは常に注目される仕事ですから……\nある意味、休みなどないと思っていただかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being an idol means being in the spotlight all the time…\nIn a way‚ you gotta act like there ain't no days off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "特に、mihoさんは最年長な訳ですから\nステージの外でも、模範になっていただきたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially since you're the eldest in the group‚ miho-san.\nOffstage too‚ we need you to set a good example.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "……はい\n……今後はこんなことがないように、気をつけます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes.\n…I'll be careful to make sure nothing like this happens again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "――で、それでですね、ツアーが終わったら\nスリクスには、長めにオフを入れる予定なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So‚ after the tour is over‚\nI'm planning to give IIIX some extended time off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "……私、別にほしいなんて言ってませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I never said I wanted time off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくですから、mihoさんも\n旅行でもなんでも行って、リフレッシュして来て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a good chance for you too‚ miho-san.\nTake a trip or whatever‚ just go and refresh yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.6086222827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "……いきなり、そんなこと言われても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sudden like this‚ I don't know what to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2,
      "sfxList": []
