      "text": "……うう……\n実は、本番中も少し気分が悪かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh…\nActually‚ I felt a bit off during the performance‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "本番中は集中してて気にならなかったんですけど\n宿に戻ってから、酷くなってきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was focused during the show so I didn't notice‚ but\nAfter we got back to the lodge‚ it got worse…",
        "id": ""
