      "text": "まだ二日酔いが残ってるんですか？\nfranさんといい、一体どれだけ飲んだんですか！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still feeling the effects of the hangover?\nBetween you and Fran-san‚ how much did y'all drink?!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
