      "text": "おつまみはカロリーが高いからなるべく避けてますし\nお酒を飲むのも、付き合いで少しでしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I usually avoid snacks since they're high in calories‚\nAnd I only drink a little‚ just to be sociable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "……自分が酔うとどうなるのかも\n……正直、よく知らなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I really didn't know\n…honestly‚ what it's like to be drunk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
